================================ CURRENT STATE =================================
========================== TASKS:
- lowerSpeedForResources: if some resouces not full, slow down
- speedUpIfResources: if all resources full, speed up

- changeSpeed: changeSpeedLvl

- lowerAlarmLvl: if flag:lastSeenEnemy is old lower the alarm lvl
- stayInRegion: M:goToXY

- alarmAboutSpottedEnemy: Alarm:spotEnemyFlag
- alarmAboutIncomingFire: Alarm:incomingFireFlag

- changeManouver: M:[goStraight, turnRight, turnLeft]
- changeManouver2: M1:goStraiht <-> M2:[turnRight, turnLeft]

- avoidIncomingFire: M:[turnRight, turnLeft]

- followEnemy: M:followEnemy
- followEnemyCloaked: cloak and M:followEnemy

- goAroundEnemy: M:goAroundEnemy
- goOrbit: M:goOrbit

- slowDownAndDie: slow down and do:onDie
- slowDown: slow down and do:doAtStop
- die: do:onDie
- expire: do:onExpire
- explode: do:onExplode

- regionStateOut: do:regionStateOut

- goStraight: M:goStraight

- goToStar: search nearest star and set M:goToStar
- followEnemyAroundStar: M:followEnemyAroundStar
- goRandomAroundStar: M:[iddleOnStar, turnRightOnStar, turnLeftOnStar]

- mergeSearch: if other enemy is ready to merge with M:mergeWith

- produceSquad: go around squad array and try produce some missing squad member

